  "title": "1 Year Senior Executive (Design & Content)  #NJN",
  "description": "<p>Pioneer<br />8.30am - 5.45pm (Mon - Thurs); 8.30am - 5.15pm (Fri)</p><p><strong>KEY RESPONSIBILITIES   </strong></p><ul><li>Manage school's social media platforms, including content planning, posting schedules, website and Intranet updates and website revamp.</li><li>Develop engaging, audience-focused content, including student stories, research highlights, event promotions, and scholarship features.</li><li>Design and produce marketing materials in a variety of formats, including print, video, and digital platforms.</li><li>Support outreach initiatives and events management, including postgraduate events, career fairs, and information sessions.</li><li>Provide administrative support on partnership matters and related activities.</li></ul><p><strong>\nREQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Mass Communications, Visual Communications, Graphic Design or a related field.</li><li>Proficient design and visual marketing skills with minimum 2 to 3 years’ working experience in design, video production or marcoms.</li></ul><p><br />Jessica Nguyen Huynh Thanh Truc</p><p>CEI Reg. No. R23113787</p><p>EA License No. 99C4599</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p></p>",
